&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then I updated the X11 configuration with xrdb.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre style=&quot;background-color:#002b36&quot;&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:#002b36;color:#839496;&quot;&gt;$ xrdb -load ${HOME}&#x2F;.Xresources
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
