&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;davedavenport.github.io&#x2F;rofi&#x2F;&quot;&gt;Rofi&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;, a replacement to
